>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Podcasts and Episodes</h2><h3>Episodes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/securityledger/chris-valasek-of-ioactive\">Hacking Connected Vehicles with Chris Valasek of IOActive</a> - Chris Valasek talks about hacking into connected vehicles.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Companies and Jobs</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tesla.com/careers/search#/filter/?keyword=security&#x26;department=1\">Tesla</a> - Tesla hires security professionals for a variety of roles, particularly securing their vehicles.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Companies and Jobs</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.intrepidcs.com/jobs/\">Intrepid Control Systems</a> - Embedded security company building tools for reversing vehicles.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Companies and Jobs</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rapid7.com/company/careers.jsp\">Rapid7</a> - Rapid7 does work in information, computer, and embedded security.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h1>Companies and Jobs</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.ioactive.com/\">IOActive</a> - Security consulting firm that does work on pentesting hardware and embedded systems.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T18:50:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.owasp.org/index.php/OWASP_Internet_of_Things_Project#tab=Community\">OWASP Internet of Things Project</a> - OWASP's project to secure IoT, from cars to medi