ucid/FsShelter\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - F# library for authoring <a href=\"https://storm.apache.org\">Apache Storm</a> components and topologies. Offering high-level abstractions for distributed and fault-tolerant event stream processing.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T12:50:48.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"J2TEAM/awesome-AutoIt","categoryHTML":"<h2>Useful Resources</h2><h3>Syntax Highlighter</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://prismjs.com/\">PrismJS</a> - Added AutoIt since version 1.1.0</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T12:46:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"quozd/awesome-dotnet","categoryHTML":"<h2>ORM</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Nick-Lucas/LimeBean\">Limebean</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Nick-Lucas/LimeBean\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">28</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":28,\"repo\":\"Nick-Lucas/LimeBean\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Hybrid ORM which uses SQL fragments and doesn't require Model Classes.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T12:27:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"44bits/awesome-opensource-documents","categoryHTML":"<h2>Subjects</h2><h3>World Wide Web</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>RESTful API Guidelines (<a href=\"https://zalando.github.io/restful-api-guidelines/index.html\">Site</a>, cc) - Comprehensive, \"API First\" design guidelines developed by Zalando</li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-28T11:30:32.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"xen0l/awesome-dtrace","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a